name: QRY-0032
title: Query 0032
sql:
SELECT `tabTables`.table_name AS `Table Name`,
       sum(`tabTables`.total_charges) AS `Total Charges`
  FROM `tabTables` AS `tabTables`
 INNER JOIN `tabTotal Order` AS `tabTotal Order`
    ON `tabTables`.name = `tabTotal Order`.parent
 WHERE `tabTables`.enabled = '1'
   AND `tabTotal Order`.creation BETWEEN '2024-11-12 00:00:00' AND '2024-11-12 23:59:59'
 GROUP BY `tabTables`.table_name
 LIMIT 100

name: QRY-0033
title: Query 0033
sql:
SELECT `tabTables`.*
  FROM `tabTables` AS `tabTables`
 LIMIT 100

name: QRY-0034
title: Query 0034
sql:
SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN t.total_charges = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS total_vacant_count,
       SUM(CASE WHEN t.total_charges > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS total_occupied_count
  FROM `tabTables` t
  LEFT JOIN `tabTotal Order` o
    ON o.parent = t.name
   AND o.creation >= CURDATE()
 WHERE t.enabled = 1

name: QRY-0035
title: Query 0035
sql:
SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN t.total_charges = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS total_vacant_count,
       SUM(CASE WHEN t.total_charges > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS total_occupied_count
  FROM `tabTables` t
  LEFT JOIN `tabTotal Order` o
    ON o.parent = t.name
   AND o.creation >= CURDATE()
 WHERE t.enabled = 1

name: QRY-0036
title: Query 0036
sql:
SELECT `tabTables`.table_name AS `Table Name`,
       COALESCE(SUM(`tabTables`.total_charges), 0) AS `Total Charges`
  FROM `tabTables`
  LEFT JOIN `tabTotal Order`
    ON `tabTables`.name = `tabTotal Order`.parent
   AND `tabTotal Order`.creation = curdate()
 WHERE `tabTables`.enabled = '1'
   AND `tabTables`.total_charges > 0
 GROUP BY `tabTables`.table_name
